<h1>Chapter 5</h1>
<h2> Fire Alarm </h2>
When Steve was at bed at night time, he heard fire alarm around his house and at that time he get up to his bed.
After he get up, he tried to look out with his window, but he did not heared firm alarm anymore, and he decided back to his bed.
During that time, Steve was very confused because he did not know what happened to his village and he wait his bed to konw the problem.
When he was at bed, he heard the second firm alarm sound and he tried to go out from his bed fastly and look out around his house.
He saw many fire workers with their fire equipment and he go to there, asked them what happend? and they responded to him their was fire and now we controlled it.
The fire alarm location was in front of Steve house, but he didn't considered it happened in front of his house and then he went back to his house.
